      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CUMBRIA CHRISSY (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with two wins and two minors from five tries. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (29.80) in a NG, finishing a 5 length sixth. Looks well placed and should feature. ZIPPING HOPKINS (5) impressed when clocking an excellent 29.62 over 520m at Wentworth Park three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Top win three back and can measure up again. SQUARE UP (2) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 5.5 lengths fifth (22.72) last time in a Grade 3/4 at Bulli over 400m. Has the ability and looks a key chance. SKEDADDLE ARLO (8) has a solid strike rate at this track and distance.",
